@item 52 @tab @code{getpeername} @tab Reports the connected peer pathname or
IPv4 address and port where available.
@item 53 @tab @code{socketpair} @tab Builds a connected Unix-domain stream
pair.
@item 54 @tab @code{setsockopt} @tab Accepts options as compatibility no-ops on
socket descriptors.
@item 55 @tab @code{getsockopt} @tab Returns a zero integer value for
